      "content": "At the heart of SNOs are five entities:\n\n1. **DAO** -- governing entity for strategic vision, on-chain governance, transparent decision-making.\n2. **Operational Hub (OH)** -- administrative core handling contributor relationships, compliance, payment processing via Swiss Associations.\n3. **Operational Collateral Fund (OCF)** -- financial infrastructure allocating resources and issuing POWTs.\n4. **Revenue Generating Hub (RGH)** -- commercial interface managing licensing, product sales, and customer-facing activities.\n5. **IP-Holding Entity (IPSPV)** -- safeguards intellectual property, enforces licensing, employs dual licensing model.",
